IEEE is a leading publisher of electrical
 
and electronics engineering papers.  IEEE is the copyright holder of over
3  
million research papers housed in our digitial library IEEE Xplore.  IEEE 

Xplore is a members only site and each article is housed behind a pay  
wall.  While not posting IEEE copyrighted content on their blog
themselves,  
Tancetexpert.blogspot.com is clearly offering to provide unauthorized  
copies of IEEE copyrighted material to users for free.  Comments on the  
blog's sole post demonstrate that users are asking for IEEE copyrighted  
material.
